Title: NETMESSAGE:ROLL OUT
Translation: 滚石行动

Title: NETMESSAGE:Move between rotating rings\nto avoid falling into the slime!
Translation: 在旋转的圆环之间闪转腾挪\n不要掉到黏液里！

Title: NETMESSAGE:PERFECT MATCH
Translation: 完美配对

Title: NETMESSAGE:Match the icon on the screen\nto avoid the slime!
Translation: 和屏幕上的标志匹配上就能避开黏液！

Title: NETMESSAGE:STOMPIN' GROUND
Translation: 犀牛大冲撞

Title: NETMESSAGE:Avoid the charging Rhinos\nand stay inside the area!
Translation: 躲避横冲直撞的犀牛\n尽量留在场地内！

Title: NETMESSAGE:BLOCK PARTY
Translation: 砖头派对

Title: NETMESSAGE:Avoid the moving walls\nand stay on the platform!
Translation: 闪避向你冲来的墙面\n留在平台上吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:JUMP CLUB
Translation: 蹦跳俱乐部

Title: NETMESSAGE:Jump over the spinning beam\nand avoid falling into the slime!
Translation: 跳过旋转的横杆\n不要掉进黏液里！

Title: NETMESSAGE:SLIME CLIMB
Translation: 水涨爬高

Title: NETMESSAGE:Outrun the slime and reach the finish line!
Translation: 逃过上涨的岩浆，躲过各类障碍，冲向终点吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:THE WHIRLYGIG
Translation: 旋转木马

Title: NETMESSAGE:Navigate the obstacles\nand race to the finish line!
Translation: 避开障碍物冲向终点吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:SEE SAW
Translation: 跷跷板

Title: NETMESSAGE:Run and balance across rows of see-saws\nto reach the finish line!
Translation: 跑过一个又一个跷跷板\n保持平衡，冲向终点线！

Title: NETMESSAGE:DOOR DASH
Translation: 闯门冲关

Title: NETMESSAGE:Avoid the fake doors\nand race to the finish line!
Translation: 避开假门\n冲向终点吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:TIP TOE
Translation: 踮踮脚尖

Title: NETMESSAGE:Avoid the fake tiles\nand find the hidden path to reach the finish line!
Translation: 避开假的地砖\n找到通往终点线的隐藏路径吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:GATE CRASH
Translation: 五花八门

Title: NETMESSAGE:Avoid the moving doors\nand race to the finish line!
Translation: 避开移动的门\n冲向终点吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:HEX-A-GONE
Translation: 蜂窝迷图

Title: NETMESSAGE:Be the last Fall Guy\nstanding above the slime!
Translation: 勇敢成为最后一个\n不沾黏液的糖豆人吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:HIT PARADE
Translation: 障碍狂欢

Title: NETMESSAGE:Navigate the obstacles\nand race to the finish line!
Translation: 避开障碍物冲向终点吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:FRUIT CHUTE
Translation: 连躲带落

Title: NETMESSAGE:Dodge the flying fruits\nand race up to the finish line!
Translation: 避开飞来的水果\n在传送带上向终点狂奔吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:DIZZY HEIGHTS
Translation: 目眩山巅

Title: NETMESSAGE:FALL BALL
Translation: 激情足球

Title: NETMESSAGE:Score goals by getting balls\ninto the opposing team 's goal!
Translation: 把球弄进对手门里即可得分\n团队协作获得胜利吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:You have to decide number of games to play before starting the game!
Translation: 开始游戏前必须先选择关卡数量！

Title: NETMESSAGE:You are now act as spectator
Translation: press R to quit spectator mode!
Color: 你现在是观察者！按 R 退出观察者模式！

Title:
NETMESSAGE:Map script is not working!
You will have to get full installation of this map
and latest build of metamod-fallguys
from hzqst's github repository to get this map working.
Translation: 地图脚本加载失败，该地图必须完整安装所有资源和metamod-fallguys插件（从github下载）才可以正常运行
